      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4a5a4a; line-height: 1.7;">Alabama's deepest lake offers world-class spotted bass fishing, trophy stripers, great crappie in the spring, and catfish nearly year-round. Here's the complete picture.</p>
